AG,CAAC,GAAG,IAAI,CAAC,eAAe,CAAC,CAAC;YAChD,IAAI,CAAC,eAAe,GAAG,EAAE,CAAC;YAE1B,IAAI,CAAC;gBACH,2CAA2C;gBAC3C,OAAO,CAAC,KAAK,CAAC,+BAA+B,aAAa,CAAC,MAAM,mBAAmB,CAAC,CAAC;gBAEtF,qDAAqD;gBACrD,IAAI,CAAC,2BAA2B,CAAC,aAAa,CAAC,CAAC;YAClD,CAAC;YAAC,OAAO,KAAK,EAAE,CAAC;gBACf,OAAO,CAAC,KAAK,CAAC,+CAA+C,EAAE,KAAK,CAAC,CAAC;YACxE,CAAC;QACH,CAAC;KAAA;IAEO,2BAA2B,CAAC,MAAa;QAC/C,MAAM,aAAa,GAAG,MAAM;aACzB,MAAM,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,SAAS,KAAK,wBAAwB,IAAI,CAAC,CAAC,SAAS,KAAK,yBAAyB,CAAC,eAAe,CAAC;aAClH,GAAG,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,QAAQ,CAAC,KAAK,CAAC;aAC1B,MAAM,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC,CAAC;QAElB,IAAI,aAAa,CAAC,MAAM,GAAG,CAAC,EAAE,CAAC;YAC7B,OAAO,CAAC,KAAK,CAAC,sCAAsC,EAAE;gBACpD,aAAa,EAAE,aAAa,CAAC,MAAM;gBACnC,aAAa,EAAE,IAAI,GAAG,CAAC,aAAa,CAAC,CAAC,IAAI;aAC3C,CAAC,CAAC;QACL,CAAC;IACH,CAAC;CACF;AAED,qDAAqD;AACrD,MAAM,CAAC,MAAM,mBAAmB,GAAG;IACjC,yBAAyB;IACzB,6BAA6B;IAC7B,0BAA0B;IAC1B,4BAA4B;IAC5B,yBAAyB;IACzB,2BAA2B;CAC5B,CAAC",
